title: COUNTER-STRIKE 1.6 EXTREME
description:
Counter Strike 1.6 Extreme is a CS 1.6 freeware freeware kit . It's a pretty old kit and is preferred by many players. It is abbreviated as cs 1.6 xtcs . It brings improved graphics and a more accessible gameplay for beginner CS 1.6 players. The CS is altered in its totality being skimmed: the skin, the textures and the sounds. Cs is unzipped anywhere on the disk and can be started on the icon. The game will start and then you can shoot with enemies on various maps. The kit is one of the oldest but still played by 1.6 older players. This cs 1.6 contains boots, you have the option if you want boots or not.
